hadiths[11]{hadithnumber,text}:
4009,Ummul-momenin Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hammaam (ijtimae aur awaami ghusl-khaanon) mein janey se mana farmaya. magar baad mein mardon ko ijazat de-di ke chadar baandh kar ja saktey hain.  doosron ke samney nange na hon.
4010,"Janab Abu-Maleeh (Aamir bin Usama (Rahimahullah)) se riwayat hai ke shaam ki kuchh aurten Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ke paas aaeen . unhoney puchha ke tum kin logon mein se ho? unhoney kaha : ham ahle-Sham mein se hain. unhoney kaha : shayad tum us ilaqey ki ho jahan ki aurten hammaam mein jati hain? aurton ne kaha : haan ! to Sayeda Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : aagah raho ! beshak maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''jo koi aurat apney ghar ke alawa kahin aur apney kapdey utarti hai wo apney aur Allah taala ke beech jo (izzat aur karaamat ka ( parda hai, usko phaad deti hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke ye Jarir ki riwayat hai aur ziyada kamil hai. magar Jarir ne Abu-Maleeh (قال قال رسول الله ﷺ) ka zikr nahin kiya. (mursal bayan kiya)."
4011,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''an-qareeb tumharey liye ajam ke ilaqey Fateh hongey aur tum wahan aisey gharondey pao gey jinhen ''hammaam'' kaha jata hoga. to mard un mein hergiz na jaeyn siwaey iske ke chadaren baandh kar (baa-parda ho kar jaeyn) aur aurton ko un se mana karna siwaye iskey ke koi bimar ho ya nifaas mein ho.''"
4012,"Hazrat Yaala bin Umayya (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne eik aadmi ko dekha ke wo eik khuli jagah mein kapda baandhey baghair naha raha tha to aap member par chadhey aur Shan Wale Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki, phir farmaya : ''Shan Wala Allah intehai haya wala aur parda posh hai, haya aur parda poshi ko pasand karta hai, so tum mein se jab koi ghusl kerney lagey , to parda kar ley.''"
4013,Safwan bin Yaala apney walid se wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se yehi hadees riwayat kartey hain. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : pehli riwayat ziyada kamil hai.
4014,"Janab Jur'aa apney walid Abdur-Rehman bin Jarhad se riwayat kartey hain aur ye Jarhad (Raziallahu anhu) as-haabe suffa mein se they. unhoney bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey yahan baithey huey they aur meri raan nangi ho rahi thi , to aapney farmaya : ''kya tumhen maloom nahin ke raan qabile-satar hoti hai.'' (yani isey chhupana chahiye.)"
4015,"Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''apni raan ko nanga mat kar aur kisi doosrey ki raan ko mat dekh , zinda ho ya murda. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain is hadees mein zauf (kamzori) hai."
4016,"Hazrat Miswar bin Makhrima (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke main (eik baar) eik bhari pathar uthaey chala ja raha tha ke mera kapda gir gaya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''apney ooper kapda ley lo aur barahna (nange) ho kar mat chalo.''"
4017,"Janab Behaz bin Hakeem apney walid se wo dada ( Muawiya bin Haida ( se riwayat kartey hain wo kehtey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aap hamein hamarey satron ke baarey mein kya farmatey hain, kya ikhtiyar keren aur kya choden ? (yani kis se chupaeyn aur kis se na chupaeyn ?) aapney farmaya : ''apni sharmgaah (aur satar) ki hifazat karo, sirf biwi ya londi se ijazat hai.'' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! jab log aapas mein miley juley baithey hon to? aapney farmaya : ''jahan tak ho sakey koi tera sattar hergiz na dekhay.'' maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! ham mein se jab koi akela ho to? aapney farmaya : ''logon ki nisbat Allah uska ziyada haqdaar hai ke us se haya ki jaey.''"
4018,Janab Abdur-Rehman bin Abu-Saeed Khudri apney walid Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi mard kisi doosrey mard ka sattar na dekhay aur na koi aurat kisi dusri aurat ka sattar dekhay. na koi mard kisi doosrey mard ke sath eik kapdey mein letey aur na koi aurat dusri aurat ke sath eik kapdey mein letey.''
4019,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi mard doosrey mard ke sath ya koi aurat dusri aurat ke sath hergiz na letey , magar beta ya baap ho to jayez hai.'' raawi ne kaha ke teesri baat bhi zikr ki thi jo main bhool gaya."
